Hudson's Bay Co said it agreed to sellits entire 54.5 pct interest in Canadian Roxy Petroleum Ltd, atotal of about 7.5 mln shares, to Westcoast Transmission Co Ltd&lt;WTC> for 11 dlrs a share.    Hudson's Bay said proceeds of about 82 mln dlrs will beused to reduce corporate debt. It said the sale was part of aprogram of concentrating on its core business of departmentstores and real estate.    The sale is subject to regulatory approvals. Reuter&#3;